00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:10.110
wasn't actually in Drive.

00:15:10.110 --> 00:15:11.270
It's still on their desktop.

00:15:11.270 --> 00:15:14.630
Well, they can just switch over
to upload, drag it right

00:15:14.630 --> 00:15:15.180
on to there.

00:15:15.180 --> 00:15:18.220
It will upload to Drive, and
then we'll send that file

00:15:18.220 --> 00:15:20.830
information to your app where
you can write appropriately

00:15:20.830 --> 00:15:22.080
direct in the cloud.

00:15:25.290 --> 00:15:28.690
So that's basically
the Picker.

00:15:28.690 --> 00:15:33.090
It's actually really easy to use
this in your application.

00:15:33.090 --> 00:15:33.900
So this is the code.

00:15:33.900 --> 00:15:36.950
The first thing that you need
to do is just include our

00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:38.070
loader script.

00:15:38.070 --> 00:15:43.340
That's at google.com/jsapi.

00:15:43.340 --> 00:15:44.420
That's just a generic loader.

00:15:44.420 --> 00:15:47.290
We have to tell it to load
the Picker library.

00:15:47.290 --> 00:15:49.590
