00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:43.430
how easy it is for people
to share content.

00:20:43.430 --> 00:20:47.710
And for those of you that use
Drive today, you've probably

00:20:47.710 --> 00:20:50.310
seen a dialogue like this
whenever you tried to share.

00:20:50.310 --> 00:20:53.490
You see this inside the editors
as well, inside docs

00:20:53.490 --> 00:20:54.985
and spreadsheets and
