00:21:22.450 --> 00:21:24.850
request permission to
all of the content

00:21:24.850 --> 00:21:26.660
in the user's Drive.

00:21:26.660 --> 00:21:30.230
So it puts you in a hard place
of choosing between enabling

00:21:30.230 --> 00:21:33.060
all these features like being
able to manipulate ACLs and

00:21:33.060 --> 00:21:37.170
share files, while still
trying to use the least

00:21:37.170 --> 00:21:40.580
permissive scope possible that
makes sense for your app.

00:21:40.580 --> 00:21:44.900
So we actually have a brand new
feature, and actually it

